{"tid":1333474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果A1: 警打壓721遊行 終點修頓禁往金鐘","createTime":"2019-07-19T16:57:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T09:28:44.000Z","uid":240362,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a3d81b5ac7c3079dc0e0b588a2afa1b7b922c25b","tid":1333474,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:57:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67402936_10157857795557448_4053315445036417024_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_oc=AQm_Njd7guYs2_rxS1TalHH9zk0x1UenAGAcPO8G5hKVn9cXN539_V15Gx2aDtxfDuk&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=40917b630c3a577b627b6db621cdcec0&amp;oe=5DEC5361\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67402936_10157857795557448_4053315445036417024_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_oc%3DAQm_Njd7guYs2_rxS1TalHH9zk0x1UenAGAcPO8G5hKVn9cXN539_V15Gx2aDtxfDuk%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D40917b630c3a577b627b6db621cdcec0%26oe%3D5DEC5361&h=34e2fc61&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf96e89063848cf050bd8bf6a0622a75a42adea4","tid":1333474,"uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:57:42.000Z","msg":"【A1頭條】持續個多月遍地開花的反送中遊行，未能撼動特首林鄭月娥不撤回、不徹查、不撤控、不下台的決心，政府反而借網絡流傳的「消息」，收緊港人遊行自由。民陣發起明天維園至中環的大遊行，原定路線及時間均被警方否決；警方將遊行路線縮短至以灣仔修頓球場附近為終點，禁止遊行隊伍經過金鐘及中環，又規定遊行必須在晚上9時結束，變相令參加人數減少。民陣批評警方限制和平集會無助阻止衝突，今天會向遊行上訴委員會提出上訴。"},{"pid":"4ec5a984e0121e29a6ad66e3e3347ee3dea36daf","tid":1333474,"uid":124894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:57:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721見</span></span>"},{"pid":"63ab4450d493330b57d6b5193dfbdb8f43f19df0","tid":1333474,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ec5a984e0121e29a6ad66e3e3347ee3dea36daf","tid":1333474,"uid":124894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:57:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-